'''Ziyad Mubarak Eid Al-Marwani Al-Johani''' ({{langx|ar|زياد مبارك المرواني الجهني}}; born 11 November 2001) is a Saudi Arabian professional [[football (soccer)|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[Al-Ahli Saudi FC|Al-Ahli]] and the [[Saudi Arabia national football team|Saudi Arabia national team]].<ref>{{cite web |title=زياد مبارك الجهني - Zaid Al-Johani|url=https://www.kooora.com/?player=139152}}</ref><ref name="soccerway">{{cite web |title=ZIYAD AL-JOHANI |url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/ziyad-aljohani/662796/}}</ref>

==Career==
Al-Johani started his career at the youth teams of [[Al-Ahli Saudi FC|Al-Ahli]]. He was first called up to the first team after the 2019–20 season resumed following the COVID-19 pandemic. He signed his first professional contract for the club on 8 August 2020.<ref>{{cite web |title=رسمياً..أهلي جدة يوقع عقداً احترافياً مع زياد الجهني لـ4 سنوات |url=https://kora.com/news/226575-%D8%B1%D8%B3%D9%85%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%A3%D9%87%D9%84%D9%8A-%D8%AC%D8%AF%D8%A9-%D9%8A%D9%88%D9%82%D8%B9-%D8%B9%D9%82%D8%AF%D8%A7-%D8%A7%D8%AD%D8%AA%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%81%D9%8A%D8%A7-%D9%85%D8%B9-%D8%B2%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%AF-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AC%D9%87%D9%86%D9%8A-%D9%84%D9%804-%D8%B3%D9%86%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%AA }}{{Dead link|date=September 2025 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref> He was then named on the bench for the first time in the [[Ittihad F.C.–Al-Ahli F.C. rivalry|derby match]] against [[Al-Ittihad Club (Jeddah)|Al-Ittihad]] a day later. He made his first-team on 30 May 2021 in the final league match of the season against [[Ettifaq FC|Al-Ettifaq]].<ref>{{cite web |title=تعرف على تشكيلة الأهلي لمباراة الاتفاق |url=https://sa.hihi2.com/2021/05/30/p148068.html}}</ref> On 24 July 2022, Al-Johani renewed his contract with Al-Ahli until the end of the 2025–26 season.<ref>{{cite web |title=الأهلي يجدد عقد زياد الجهني حتى 2026م |url=https://www.alriyadh.com/1963106}}</ref>

==International career==
In June 2023, he took part in the [[Maurice Revello Tournament]] in France<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.tournoimauricerevello.com/smartphone/festival/archives/joueurs.php?annee=2023| title=Festival International Espoirs Football Tournoi Maurice Revello Toulon| publisher=Maurice Revello Tournament| website=tournoimauricerevello.com| language=fr| accessdate=14 May 2025}}</ref> with Saudi Arabia.

